    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s looking for a brand-new home. This car has been so reliable for me and is still in really solid shape\u2014perfect for daily commutes or weekend getaways. It\u2019s been well-cared for, runs beautifully, and is ready to hit the road with its next owner. If you\u2019re looking for a dependable car that won't let you down, this is the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
