    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically robust E46 M3, a definitive expression of the S54 inline-six architecture. This high-revving powerplant utilizes individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing to produce a broad, linear powerband. The 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox ensures tactile engagement, directing power through a variable M-differential lock. Recent preventative maintenance includes reinforced rear subframe mounts and rod bearing replacement, ensuring structural and internal longevity. With sharp turn-in via its M-tuned suspension and excellent pedal feel, this chassis remains a benchmark for analog performance. A well-sorted example ready for the spirited driver.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_3",
