    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle strikes the perfect balance between performance and daily utility. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish, though close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front hood and a small, superficial scratch near the rear wheel well\u2014honest wear for a car that has been carefully driven. Inside, the cabin remains a premium environment; the leather upholstery is clean and free of tears, showing only light creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. Every electronic component, from the intuitive infotainment system to the heated seats and backup camera, is in full working order. Mechanically, the engine pulls smoothly and the transmission shifts seamlessly, with no warning lights on the dash. I have kept a detailed log of all scheduled maintenance and oil changes. This is a solid, reliable car that is ready for its next owner. I welcome any independent inspections to verify its condition and performance.",
