    {
      "id": "sybil_16_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "Offering a driver-spec E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54B32 naturally aspirated inline-six. This high-string powerplant utilizes individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS to provide a broad, linear torque curve and an 8,000 RPM redline. Power is routed through a traditional 6-speed manual transmission to a factory limited-slip differential. This example is mechanically sound with a documented rear subframe reinforcement and recent valve adjustment. While the exterior shows minor patina expected of a well-loved performance vehicle, the suspension geometry remains sharp with refreshed bushings and dampers, ensuring the chassis maintains its legendary communicative feedback.",
